msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "Selamat Datang"

msgid "Select an Option"
msgstr "Pilih satu Opsi"

msgid "Easily create a backup image of your computer, or completely restore from one.  Click an option to begin:"
msgstr ""
"Buat image cadangan dari komputer Anda dengan mudah, atau pulihkan sebuah "
"image sepenuhnya.  Klik sebuah opsi untuk memulai:"

msgid "Backup"
msgstr "Cadangkan"

msgid "Restore"
msgstr "Pulihkan"

msgid "Verify Image"
msgstr "Verifikasi Image"

msgid "Need help? Start by checking the Rescuezilla frequently asked questions, then proceed to the Rescuezilla forum."
msgstr ""
"Butuh bantuan? Mulai dengan memeriksa pertanyaan yang sering ditanyakan "
"Rescuezilla, setelahnya lanjut ke forum Rescuezilla."

msgid "Consider contributing $1/month on the crowdfunding website Patreon so Rescuezilla can continue to be developed."
msgstr ""
"Pertimbangkan berkontribusi $1/bulan di situs penggalangan dana Patreon "
"sehingga Rescuezilla dapat terus dikembangkan."

msgid "Back"
msgstr "Kembali"

msgid "Next >"
msgstr "Lanjut >"

msgid "Please wait…"
msgstr "Harap tunggu…"

msgid "Identifying disk drives…"
msgstr "Mengidentifikasi disk drives…"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Unmounting: {path}"
msgstr "Melepas: {path}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Unable to unmount {path}"
msgstr "Tidak dapat melepas {path}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Running: {app}"
msgstr "Menjalankan: {app}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Running {app} on {device}"
msgstr "Menjalankan {app} pada {device}"

msgid "Failed to run command: "
msgstr "Gagal menjalankan perintah: "

msgid "Error querying drives: "
msgstr "Galat saat mengkueri drive: "

msgid "Clone"
msgstr "Klon"

msgid "Step 1: Understanding Cloning"
msgstr "Langkah 1: Memahami Kloning"

msgid "Please understand how \"cloning\" differs from \"imaging\"."
msgstr "Tolong pahami bagaimana \"kloning\" berbeda dari \"pencitraan\"."

msgid "This mode is for \"disk cloning\". Cloning means copying one drive and directly overwriting another drive. This is a direct one-step operation with no temporary storage required.\n"
"\n"
"Cloning is different to \"disk imaging\". Imaging means copying everything from one drive into very large files stored inside a folder on an external drive. Multiple images can be saved on the same external drive. These images can be restored back to the original disk, or to additional disks. In other words, for \"imaging\" the backup operation copies your drive to <i>files</i> that need to be stored on a drive at least temporarily before it can be restored.\n"
"\n"
""
"To use the \"imaging\" wizards, click <b>Back</b> and select <b>Backup</b> or <b>Restore</b>."
msgstr ""
"Mode ini digunakan untuk \"kloning disk\". Kloning berarti menyalin satu "
"drive dan menimpanya langsung ke drive lain. Ini adalah operasi langsung "
"satu langkah tanpa memerlukan penyimpanan sementara.\n"
"\n"
"Kloning berbeda dengan \"pencitraan disk\". Pencitraan berarti menyalin "
"semua data dari satu drive ke dalam file-file yang sangat besar yang "
"disimpan di dalam folder pada drive eksternal. Banyak pencitraan dapat "
"disimpan di drive eksternal yang sama. Pencitraan ini dapat dikembalikan ke "
"disk asli, atau ke disk tambahan lainnya. Dengan kata lain, untuk "
"\"pencitraan\", operasi pencadangan menyalin drive Anda ke <i>file</i> yang "
"perlu disimpan di drive setidaknya untuk sementara sebelum dapat "
"dikembalikan.\n"
"\n"
"Untuk menggunakan wizard \"pencitraan\", klik <b>Kembali</b> dan pilih <b>"
"Cadangkan</b> atau <b>Pulihkan</b>."

msgid "To begin the \"cloning\" wizard, click <b>Next</b>"
msgstr "Untuk memulai wizard \"kloning\", klik <b>Berikutnya</b>"

msgid "Step 2: Select Source Drive"
msgstr "Langkah 2: Pilih Asal Drive"

msgid "Select the <b>source drive</b> to clone."
msgstr "Pilih <b>drive sumber</b> untuk dikloning."

msgid "Select the <b>destination drive</b> to overwrite."
msgstr "Pilih <b>drive tujuan</b> untuk ditimpa."

msgid "Step 4: Select Partitions to Clone"
msgstr "Langkah 4: Pilih Partisi untuk Dikloning"

msgid "Select which partitions from the source drive to clone, and whether to overwrite the partition table. <b>Leave everything selected to completely clone the source drive to the destination drive.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Pilih partisi mana dari drive sumber yang akan dikloning, dan apakah akan "
"menimpa tabel partisi. <b>Biarkan semuanya terpilih untuk mengkloning "
"seluruh drive sumber ke drive tujuan.</b>"

msgid "Step 5: Confirm Cloning Configuration"
msgstr "Langkah 5: Konfirmasi Konfigurasi Kloning"

msgid "Confirm the following cloning configuration."
msgstr "Konfirmasi konfigurasi kloning berikut."

msgid "Cloning the following partitions"
msgstr "Mengkloning partisi berikut"

msgid "To start cloning, click <b>Next</b>."
msgstr "Untuk memulai kloning, klik <b>Berikutnya</b>."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Are you sure you want to clone the drive to {destination_drive}? Doing so will permanently overwrite data on this drive!"
msgstr ""
"Yakin ingin mengkloning drive ke {destination_drive}? Melakukannya akan "
"menimpa data di drive ini secara permanen!"

msgid "Step 6: Cloning Disk"
msgstr "Langkah 6: Mengkloning Disk"

msgid "Cloning the drive you selected.  This may take an hour or more depending on the speed of your computer and the amount of data."
msgstr ""
"Mengkloning drive yang Anda pilih.  Ini mungkin memakan waktu satu jam atau "
"lebih tergantung pada kecepatan komputer Anda dan jumlah data."

msgid "Summary of Clone"
msgstr "Ringkasan Kloning"

msgid "Clone Summary"
msgstr "Ringkasan Klon"

msgid "Confirm the clone summary."
msgstr "Konfirmasi ringkasan kloning."

msgid "Unable to shutdown Image Explorer"
msgstr "Tidak dapat menghentikan Image Explorer"

msgid "Step 1: Select Drive To Backup"
msgstr "Langkah 1: Pilih Drive Yang Ingin Dicadangkan"

msgid "Select the <b>source drive</b> that you would like to create a backup image from."
msgstr "Pilih <b>drive sumber</b> tempat Anda ingin membuat gambar cadangan."

msgid "Drive"
msgstr "Drive"

msgid "Capacity"
msgstr "Kapasitas"

msgid "Drive Model"
msgstr "Model Drive"

msgid "Serial Number"
msgstr "Nomor Seri"

msgid "Partitions"
msgstr "Partisi"

msgid "Show hidden devices (for advanced users)"
msgstr "Tampilkan perangkat tersembunyi (untuk pengguna tingkat lanjut)"

msgid "Step 2: Select Partitions to Save"
msgstr "Langkah 2: Pilih Partisi yang Ingin Disimpan"

msgid "Select which partitions to create a backup of. <b>Leave all partitions selected if you are unsure.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Pilih partisi yang ingin dicadangkan. <b>Biarkan semuanya terpilih jika Anda "
"kurang yakin.</b>"

msgid "Save"
msgstr "Simpan"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Keterangan"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Drive {drive_number}"
msgstr "Drive {drive_number}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Partition {partition_number}"
msgstr "Partisi {partition_number}"

msgid "Step 3: Select Destination Drive"
msgstr "Langkah 3: Pilih Drive Tujuan"

msgid "Click on the box below to select the source drive that you would like to create a backup image from."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada kotak di bawah ini untuk memilih drive sumber yang ingin Anda buat "
"image cadangannya."

msgid "Connected directly to my computer"
msgstr "Langsung terhubung dengan komputer saya"

msgid "Shared over a network"
msgstr "Dibagikan melalui jaringan"

msgid "Where would you like to save the image?"
msgstr "Di mana Anda ingin menyimpan image?"

msgid "Windows shared folder (SMB/CIFS, Samba)"
msgstr "Folder bersama Windows (SMB/CIFS, Samba)"

msgid "Search network"
msgstr "Cari jaringan"

msgid "Server"
msgstr "Server"

msgid "Share location (UNC path)"
msgstr "Bagikan lokasi (UNC path)"

msgid "Username"
msgstr "Nama pengguna"

msgid "Password"
msgstr "Kata sandi"

msgid "Domain"
msgstr "Domain"

msgid "Version"
msgstr "Versi"

msgid "default (Negotiate highest SMB2+ supported by client and server)"
msgstr ""
"default (Negosiasikan SMB2+ tertinggi yang didukung oleh klien dan server)"

msgid "1.0 (The classic CIFS/SMBv1 protocol)"
msgstr "1.0 (Protokol CIFS/SMBv1 klasik)"

msgid "2.0 (Introduced in Vista SP1, Windows Server 2008)"
msgstr "2.0 (Diperkenalkan pada Vista SP1, Windows Server 2008)"

msgid "2.1 (Introduced in Windows 7, Windows Server 2008R2)"
msgstr "2.1 (Diperkenalkan pada Windows 7, Windows Server 2008 R2)"

msgid "3 (The SMBv3.0 protocol version and above)"
msgstr "3 (Protokol SMBv3.0 dan versi di atasnya)"

msgid "3.0 (Introduced in Windows 8, Windows Server 2012)"
msgstr "3.0 (Diperkenalkan pada Windows 8, Windows Server 2012)"

msgid "3.0.2 (Introduced in Windows 8.1, Windows Server 2012R2)"
msgstr "3.0.2 (Diperkenalkan pada Windows 8.1, Windows Server 2012 R2)"

msgid "3.1.1 (Introduced in Windows 10, Windows Server 2016)"
msgstr "3.1.1 (Diperkenalkan pada Windows 10, Windows Server 2016)"

msgid "Unspecified (Tries NFS v4.2 first, then negotiates with server down until finds a supported version)"
msgstr ""
"Tidak Ditentukan (Mencoba NFS v4.2 terlebih dahulu, kemudian melakukan "
"negosiasi dengan server ke bawah hingga menemukan versi yang didukung)"

msgid "NFSv3"
msgstr "NFSv3"

msgid "NFSv4"
msgstr "NFSv4"

msgid "Remote path"
msgstr "Path jarak jauh"

msgid "Exported path"
msgstr "Path yang diekspor"

msgid "Identity File"
msgstr "Berkas Identitas"

msgid "Port"
msgstr "Port"

msgid "Select network-shared storage location:"
msgstr "Pilih lokasi penyimpanan jaringan-bersama:"

msgid "Select the partition where the image files will be saved to"
msgstr "Pilih partisi tempat file image akan disimpan"

msgid "Partition"
msgstr "Partisi"

msgid "Mounting…"
msgstr "Memasang…"

msgid "Close this popup to cancel the mount operation."
msgstr "Tutup popup ini untuk membatalkan operasi pemasangan."

msgid "Please ensure the username, password and other fields provided are correct, and try again."
msgstr ""
"Harap pastikan nama pengguna, kata sandi, dan bidang lain yang disediakan "
"sudah benar, dan coba lagi."

msgid "Must provide either password or SSH identity file."
msgstr "Harus memberikan kata sandi atau file identitas SSH."

msgid "Scanning folder for backup images…"
msgstr "Memindai folder untuk image cadangan…"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "({timeout_seconds} second timeout)"
msgstr "(batas waktu {timeout_seconds} detik)"

msgid "Close this popup to cancel scanning the selected folder and subfolders."
msgstr ""
"Tutup popup ini untuk membatalkan pemindaian folder dan subfolder yang "
"dipilih."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Scanning: {filename}"
msgstr "Pemindaian: {filename}"

msgid "Error processing the following images:"
msgstr "Kesalahan saat memproses image berikut:"

msgid "Unable to fully process the image associated with the following partitions:"
msgstr ""
"Tidak dapat sepenuhnya memproses image yang terkait dengan partisi berikut:"

msgid "Unable to fully process the following image:"
msgstr "Tidak dapat sepenuhnya memproses image berikut:"

msgid "Cannot find partition's associated partclone image"
msgstr "Tidak dapat menemukan bagian klon image yang terkait dengan partisi"

msgid "This can happen when loading images which Clonezilla was unable to completely backup."
msgstr ""
"Ini dapat terjadi saat memuat image yang tidak dapat dicadangkan sepenuhnya "
"oleh Clonezilla."

msgid "Note: This image format cannot distinguish between failed partclone backup and a user who chose not to backup a partition."
msgstr ""
"Catatan: Format pencitraan ini tidak dapat membedakan antara cadangan "
"partclone yang gagal dan pengguna yang memilih untuk tidak mencadangkan "
"suatu partisi."

msgid "Any other filesystems within the image should be restorable as normal."
msgstr ""
"Sistem file lain di dalam pencitraan seharusnya dapat dipulihkan seperti "
"biasa."

msgid "Needs decryption"
msgstr "Memerlukan dekripsi"

msgid "Unknown filesystem"
msgstr "Sistem file tidak dikenal"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "The backup's extended partition information is empty. If the backup contains an extended partition this will not restore correctly. All data is still fully recoverable but manual intervention is required to fully restore data within the extended partition. Please consult {url} for information and assistance."
msgstr ""
"Informasi partisi extended dari cadangan ini kosong. Jika cadangan berisi "
"partisi extended, ini tidak akan dipulihkan dengan benar. Semua data masih "
"dapat dipulihkan sepenuhnya tetapi diperlukan intervensi manual untuk "
"memulihkan data di dalam partisi extended secara utuh. Silakan kunjungi "
"{url} untuk informasi dan bantuan."

msgid "The backup's bootloader data is shorter than expected. If the backup contained certain bootloaders like GRUB, during a restore operation Rescuezilla will try and re-install the bootloader."
msgstr ""
"Data bootloader dari cadangan ini lebih pendek dari yang diharapkan. Jika "
"cadangan berisi bootloader tertentu seperti GRUB, selama operasi pemulihan "
"Rescuezilla akan mencoba memasang ulang bootloader."

msgid "Step 4: Select Destination Folder"
msgstr "Langkah 4: Pilih Folder Tujuan"

msgid "Click <b>Browse</b> to select the folder on the destination drive where your new backup image will be saved.\n"
"\n"
"The folder a backup is saved in is usually a description of the computer, e.g. <b>office1</b> or <b>zack-laptop</b>."
msgstr ""
"Klik <b>Jelajahi</b> untuk memilih folder di drive tujuan tempat pencitraan "
"cadangan baru Anda akan disimpan.\n"
"\n"
"Folder tempat cadangan disimpan biasanya berupa deskripsi dari komputer, "
"misalnya <b>office1</b> atau <b>zack-laptop</b>."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "You must select a folder inside {location}"
msgstr "Anda harus memilih folder di dalam {location}"

msgid "Please select a different folder."
msgstr "Pilih folder lain."

msgid "The table below lists the backup images that are already in this folder (if any)."
msgstr ""
"Tabel di bawah ini menampilkan pencitraan cadangan yang sudah ada di folder "
"ini (jika ada)."

msgid "Browse…"
msgstr "Jelajahi…"

msgid "Filename"
msgstr "Nama berkas"

msgid "Size"
msgstr "Ukuran"

msgid "Last modified"
msgstr "Terakhir dimodifikasi"

msgid "When you are happy with the destination folder, click <b>Next</b>."
msgstr "Jika Anda sudah siap dengan folder tujuan, klik <b>Berikutnya</b>."

msgid "Step 5: Name Your Backup"
msgstr "Langkah 5: Beri Nama Cadangan Anda"

msgid "Provide a unique name for this backup image, such as the date.  Today's date is automatically entered for you below.\n"
"\n"
"You may only use letters, numbers, and dashes in your backup name."
msgstr ""
"Berikan nama unik untuk pencitraan cadangan ini, misalnya tanggal. Tanggal "
"hari ini akan diisi secara otomatis di bawah.\n"
"\n"
"Anda hanya dapat menggunakan huruf, angka, dan tanda pisah pada nama "
"cadangan."

msgid "Optional: Provide a short description."
msgstr "Opsional: Berikan deskripsi singkat."

msgid "Step 6: Customize Compression Settings"
msgstr "Langkah 6: Sesuaikan Pengaturan Kompresi"

msgid "Customize image compression settings. <b>Don't make any changes if you are unsure.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan pengaturan kompresi pencitraan. <b>Jangan ubah apa pun jika Anda "
"tidak yakin.</b>"

msgid "Compression format: "
msgstr "Format kompresi: "

msgid "gzip"
msgstr "gzip"

msgid "default"
msgstr "bawaan"

msgid "zstandard"
msgstr "zstandard"

msgid "Uncompressed (Suitable for use with Image Explorer)"
msgstr "Tidak Terkompresi (Cocok digunakan dengan Image Explorer)"

msgid "Compression level: "
msgstr "Level kompresi: "

msgid "Fastest"
msgstr "Tercepat"

msgid "Best"
msgstr "Terbaik"

msgid "When you are happy with the compression settings, click <b>Next</b>."
msgstr "Jika pengaturan kompresi sudah sesuai, klik <b>Berikutnya</b>."

msgid "Step 7: Confirm Backup Configuration"
msgstr "Langkah 7: Konfirmasi Konfigurasi Cadangan"

msgid "Source drive"
msgstr "Drive sumber"

msgid "Backing up the following partition(s)"
msgstr "Mencadangkan partisi berikut"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "The backup image will be written into folder {dest_dir} on {description}"
msgstr ""
"Pencitraan cadangan akan ditulis ke dalam folder {dest_dir} pada "
"{description}"

msgid "Confirm the following backup configuration."
msgstr "Konfirmasikan konfigurasi cadangan berikut."

msgid "On successful completion of the task, perform the following action: "
msgstr "Setelah tugas berhasil diselesaikan, lakukan tindakan berikut: "

msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "Tidak melakukan apa pun"

msgid "Shutdown"
msgstr "Matikan"

msgid "Reboot"
msgstr "Mulai Ulang"

msgid "Rescue: Ignore filesystem inconsistencies and bad sectors"
msgstr "Rescue: Abaikan inkonsistensi sistem file dan sektor buruk"

msgid "<b>Enabling \"Rescue\" may suppress important errors. Use with caution.</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Mengaktifkan \"Rescue\" dapat menghilangkan pesan error penting. Gunakan "
"dengan hati-hati.</b>"

msgid "To start the backup, click <b>Next</b>."
msgstr "Untuk memulai pencadangan, klik <b>Berikutnya</b>."

msgid "Step 8: Creating Backup Image"
msgstr "Langkah 8: Membuat Pencitraan Cadangan"

msgid "Backing up your system to the location you selected.  This may take an hour or more depending on the speed of your computer and the amount of data."
msgstr ""
"Mencadangkan sistem Anda ke lokasi yang telah dipilih. Proses ini mungkin "
"memerlukan waktu satu jam atau lebih tergantung pada kecepatan komputer Anda "
"dan jumlah data."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Saving: {file}"
msgstr "Menyimpan: {file}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Backup {partition_name} containing filesystem {filesystem} to {destination}"
msgstr ""
"Cadangkan {partition_name} yang berisi sistem file {filesystem} ke "
"{destination}"

msgid "Summary of Backup"
msgstr "Ringkasan Pencadangan"

msgid "Confirm the backup summary."
msgstr "Konfirmasi ringkasan pencadangan."

msgid "Backup Summary"
msgstr "Ringkasan Pencadangan"

msgid "An operation is in progress. Do you wish to cancel?"
msgstr "Ada operasi yang sedang berlangsung. Apakah Anda ingin membatalkannya?"

msgid "Operation cancelled by user."
msgstr "Operasi dibatalkan oleh pengguna."

msgid "Rescue option is enabled."
msgstr "Opsi Rescue diaktifkan."

msgid "Error creating backup: "
msgstr "Kesalahan saat membuat cadangan: "

msgid "Failed to write destination file. Please confirm it is valid to create the provided file path, and try again."
msgstr ""
"Gagal menulis file tujuan. Pastikan jalur file yang diberikan valid untuk "
"dibuat, dan coba lagi."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Successful backup of swap partition {partition_name}"
msgstr "Berhasil mencadangkan partisi swap {partition_name}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "<b>Failed to backup partition</b> {partition_name}"
msgstr "<b>Gagal mencadangkan partisi</b> {partition_name}"

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Successful backup of partition {partition_name}"
msgstr "Berhasil mencadangkan partisi {partition_name}"

msgid "Backup saved successfully."
msgstr "Cadangan berhasil disimpan."

msgid "Backup succeeded with some errors:"
msgstr "Pencadangan berhasil dengan beberapa kesalahan:"

msgid "Backup operation failed:"
msgstr "Operasi pencadangan gagal:"

msgid "User requested operation to stop."
msgstr "Pengguna meminta operasi untuk dihentikan."

#, python-brace-format
msgid "Operation took {num_minutes} minutes."
msgstr "Operasi memakan waktu {num_minutes} menit."

msgid "To start a new session, click <b>Next</b>"
msgstr "Untuk memulai sesi baru, klik <b>Berikutnya</b>"

msgid "Step 1: Select Image Location"
msgstr "Langkah 1: Pilih Lokasi Pencitraan"

msgid "Where are the image files stored?"
msgstr "Di mana file pencitraan disimpan?"

msgid "Select the partition which contains the image files:"
msgstr "Pilih partisi yang berisi file pencitraan:"

msgid "Step 2: Select Backup Image"
msgstr "Langkah 2: Pilih Pencitraan Cadangan"

msgid "Click <b>Browse</b> to select the folder containing image files."
msgstr "Klik <b>Jelajahi</b> untuk memilih folder yang berisi file pencitraan."

msgid "Select the image file to restore."
msgstr "Pilih file pencitraan yang akan dipulihkan."

msgid "Step 3: Select Drive To Restore"
msgstr "Langkah 3: Pilih Drive yang Akan Dipulihkan"

msgid "Select the destination drive to restore with the selected image."
msgstr "Pilih drive tujuan untuk memulihkan dengan pencitraan yang dipilih."

msgid "Step 4: Select Partitions to Restore"
msgstr "Langkah 4: Pilih Partisi yang Akan Dipulihkan"

msgid "Select which partitions from the backup image to restore, and whether to overwrite the partition table. <b>Leave everything selected to completely restore the destination drive.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Pilih partisi mana dari pencitraan cadangan yang akan dipulihkan, dan apakah "
"akan menimpa tabel partisi. <b>Biarkan semuanya terpilih untuk memulihkan "
"seluruh drive tujuan.</b>"

msgid "Selected image"
msgstr "Pencitraan yang dipilih"

msgid "Destination partition"
msgstr "Partisi tujuan"

msgid "Overwrite partition table"
msgstr "Timpa tabel partisi"

msgid "You will be overwriting the partition table."
msgstr "Anda akan menimpa tabel partisi."

msgid "The \"destination partition\" column has been updated using the information stored within the backup image.\n\n<b>If partitions have been resized, new partitions added, or additional operating systems installed <i>since the backup image was created</i>, then the destination drive's partition table will not match the backup image, and overwriting the destination drive's partition table will render these resized and additional partitions permanently inaccessible.</b> If you have not modified the partition table in such a way since creating this backup then overwriting the partition table is completely safe and will have no negative effects."
msgstr ""
"Kolom \"partisi tujuan\" telah diperbarui menggunakan informasi yang "
"tersimpan di dalam pencitraan cadangan.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Jika partisi telah diubah ukurannya, partisi baru ditambahkan, atau "
"sistem operasi tambahan diinstal <i>sejak pencitraan cadangan dibuat</i>, "
"maka tabel partisi drive tujuan tidak akan cocok dengan pencitraan cadangan, "
"dan menimpa tabel partisi drive tujuan akan membuat partisi yang telah "
"diubah ukurannya dan partisi tambahan tersebut tidak dapat diakses secara "
"permanen.</b> Jika Anda tidak mengubah tabel partisi dengan cara seperti itu "
"sejak membuat cadangan ini, maka menimpa tabel partisi sepenuhnya aman dan "
"tidak akan menimbulkan efek negatif."

msgid "You will <b>not</b> be overwriting the partition table."
msgstr "Anda <b>tidak</b> akan menimpa tabel partisi."

msgid "The source does not contain a partition table."
msgstr "Sumber tidak berisi tabel partisi."

msgid "The \"destination partition\" column has been updated with destination drive's existing partition table information.\n\n<b>The destination partition column can be modified as a dropdown menu. Incorrectly mapping the destination partitions may cause operating systems to no longer boot.</b> If you are unsure of the mapping, consider if it's more suitable to instead overwrite the partition table."
msgstr ""
"Kolom \"partisi tujuan\" telah diperbarui dengan informasi tabel partisi "
"yang ada pada drive tujuan.\n"
"\n"
